*------------------------------( Builder: imsg )-----------------------------*

   Type:        command
   Usage:       imsg [<channelname>:] <message>
                
   Description: Send a message to an udp channel. If you want to choose a
		channel you need to specify channelname and add a colon 
	        after the channel. Further usage of imsg will send to the
		last chosen channel.

   Example:     imsg talk: Hello friends!
		imsg How are you?
   
*----------------------------------------------------------------------------*
 See also: 'istatus', 'ijoin', 'ileave', 'ilist', 'itell', 'iwho'
